        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Opioid Addiction Recovery Fraud Prevention Act of 2018</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits deceptive representation regarding the cost, price, efficacy, performance, benefit, risk, or safety of opioid treatment programs or products. </p>]]></text>
